### 🟡 SALES-02 — Three Split Annual Tables
**Tables:** `sales_2015`, `sales_2016`, `sales_2017`

**Description:**
Sales data split across 3 separate tables by year. Querying any single table produces an incomplete view of the business. Joins and aggregations fail silently if analysts query `sales_2015` alone.

| Table | Rows | Share of total |
|-------|------|---------------|
| `sales_2015` | 2,630 | 4.7% |
| `sales_2016` | 23,935 | 42.7% |
| `sales_2017` | 29,481 | 52.6% |
| **Total** | **56,046** | 100% |

**Fix applied in `stg_sales`:**
```sql
with sales_2015 as (select * from "AWDB"."dbo"."sales_2015"),
     sales_2016 as (select * from "AWDB"."dbo"."sales_2016"),
     sales_2017 as (select * from "AWDB"."dbo"."sales_2017"),
unioned as (
    select * from sales_2015
    union all select * from sales_2016
    union all select * from sales_2017
)
```

